          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"key-insights\">Key Insights</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>China reduced its extreme poverty rate from 97% in 1981 to 0% by 2019</li>\n<li>Nepal fell from 82.7% in 1984 to just 2.6% in 2022</li>\n<li>Madagascar and Mozambique have seen poverty rates above 87%, essentially unchanged for three decades</li>\n<li>Ethiopia's poverty rate dropped sharply to 16% by 2010, then rebounded to 45% by 2021 amid conflict</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
